Here is a list of joint names that are used by the Pioneer. Placing these on your Tools will make the pioneer
automatically try to mount with existing body joints.

Tool Mount Arm FG   -The hand in the foreground
Tool Mount Arm BG   -The hand in the background
Tool Mount Shoulder -Shoulder for things like Rocket launchers or shoulder mounted items
Tool Mount Back     -Joint that when the controller presses Q to store something on its back will mount to.
